# Git Push

**Every time** you complete an editing session, **push to git** for code and product docs:

1. Run `git status` - if there are uncommitted changes, stage and commit them (see exclusion below)
2. Run `git push`

**Do not** commit or push `TEACHER_QA_CHECKLIST.md` (or similar teacher QA checklists) unless the user explicitly asks. That file is for local / discussion only.

Do not end an editing session without pushing **eligible** changes. If the only changes are checklist-only, skip commit and push unless the user asked to include them.
